---



<Layout title="Web design by Valeri Ciutac">
    
    <ProjectHeader 
        projectName="Semrush" 
        projectRole="Designer Web Designer" 
        projectDate="05-2023" 
        projectImage="../../projects/semrush/semrush-header.webp" 
        projectDescription=`I designed a marketing guide and its accompanying landing page for "21 Questions to Ask When Evaluating Market Intelligence." The goal was to create a visually engaging and highly informative resource that helps marketers assess and choose the right market intelligence solutions.
My Contributions:
Guide Design – Created a structured, easy-to-read layout with clear typography, engaging visuals, and well-organized content to enhance readability and comprehension.
Landing Page Design & Development – Designed and developed a high-converting landing page to promote the guide, focusing on clear messaging, persuasive call-to-action elements, and an intuitive user experience to maximize downloads.
By combining strategic design with effective marketing principles, I ensured that the guide was both visually appealing and highly valuable for its target audience.`/>
    <FullHeightImage 
        backgroundColor="#AA2C00"
        image="../../projects/semrush/semrush-full.webp" 
            />
            <Heading title="The Objective" />
    <ContentWithMedia
    imageFirst={true}
        imageCellWidth=4
        contentCellWidth=8
        contentImage="../../projects/semrush/chats.webp"
        contentImage2="../../projects/semrush/chats_2.webp"
        imageBgColor="#000000"
        contentTitle="Stylized chat bubbles"
        contentDescription="Used as both elements for the landing page, as well as the decorative element used in the Marketing kit." 
        />
   
<Conclusion>

</Conclusion>
